wkhtmltopdf - Multi-Backend Edition
====================================

This is a fork of the wkhtmltopdf project with substantial enhancements
for modern CSS support and multi-backend rendering capabilities.

ORIGINAL PROJECT
----------------
Copyright (C) 2010-2020 wkhtmltopdf authors
Project URL: https://github.com/wkhtmltopdf/wkhtmltopdf
Original License: GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPLv3)

MULTI-BACKEND ENHANCEMENTS
--------------------------
Copyright (C) 2024-2025 wkhtmltopdf Multi-Backend Contributors
Enhancements License: GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPLv3)

Major Enhancements:
- Multi-backend architecture (Qt WebKit + Qt WebEngine)
- Full CSS3 support via Qt WebEngine (Flexbox, Grid, Transforms, etc.)
- Runtime backend selection
- HTML/CSS validator with compatibility checking
- Structured error handling system
- Comprehensive build and installation scripts
- Multiple Debian package variants (Qt5/Qt6, WebKit/WebEngine)
- Playwright wrapper for macOS compatibility
- Enhanced documentation and examples

